com.ibm.team.process.common

Interface IProcessItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAuditable, IAuditableHandle, IItem, IItemHandle, IManagedItem, IManagedItemHandle, INamed, IProcessItemHandle
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDevelopmentLine, IIteration, IIterationType, IProcessArea, IProcessAttachment, IProcessContainer, IProcessDefinition, IProjectArea, IProjectLink, IReadAccessList, ITeamArea

    public interface IProcessItem
extends IProcessItemHandle, INamed, IAuditable
    Supertype for all auditable items introduced by the team process support. Process items can be saved into the repository by using the com.ibm.team.process.internal.common.service.IProcessService
    Since:
    0.5
